:'''Asta:''' The Legion is gone, and the Curios are back. Various departments are returning to their research, and the newly imported goods from the cosmos are beginning to circulate.
:'''Asta:''' Everything is going smoothly with Project Revival. So what exactly does this letter mean?
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_2010801_8-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_2010801_8-->
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} I heard you are looking for me?
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201080104-->
:'''Asta:''' (Trailblazer), you're back. Just in time!
:'''Asta:''' Thanks to your help and everybody's hard work, the space station is pretty much back on its feet.
:'''Asta:''' As a conclusion to Project Revival, I wanted to summon you to witness the fruits of our labor.
:'''Asta:''' But just two days ago, I received a strange letter. Now that you're here, perhaps you can help me figure out what it is about.
<pre>{
