::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 112 m.ogg}} {{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 112 f.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Hello, you must be... (Trailblazer), right? How can I help you?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_100021116-->
