::{{DIcon|Talk}} I'd like to learn about the space station.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100021117-->
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 113.ogg}} '''Asta:''' This is Herta Space Station. As you might tell from its name, it belongs to the distinguished Madam Herta herself.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 114.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Herta Space Station was originally built as a warehouse for rare items and relics, but Madam Herta also allowed her followers to oversee tasks and conduct research. It then gradually turned into a scientific research base.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 115.ogg}} '''Asta:''' The storage zone you passed through contains all our inventory, and is the main research center.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 116.ogg}} '''Asta:''' The master control zone where we are now is the control center of the whole space station.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 117.ogg}} '''Asta:''' It is said that the space station also contains Madam Herta's private chamber where her most precious, rare, and dangerous collections are sealed... And for someone like her, it's not out of the realm of possibility.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 118.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Even from me, the lead researcher, there are many things she keeps secret.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} I'd like to learn about you.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100021124-->
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 119.ogg}} '''Asta:''' I'm lead researcher of Herta Space Station. But honestly... I'm more like Madam Herta's "housekeeper" of this place.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 120.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Madam Herta is a genius, but managing disparate staff, tactfully representing the space station before the Intelligentsia Guild... these are all things beyond her abilities. But as it turns out they are my forte.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 121.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Hehe, scholars are a lot easier to deal with than those vociferous old geezers back at home.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 122.ogg}} '''Asta:''' No matter how much they drone on about "Astronomy is just about looking at things, it doesn't bring any real value," they all fall silent in front of Madam Herta.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 123.ogg}} '''Asta:''' No matter the problem, you just needed to say that it was Madam Herta's wishes and all would be fine. After all, Herta herself is a symbol of wisdom.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 124.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Hey, thanks to her, I can count the stars to sleep. Otherwise, I would've had to take over the family fortune. Just thinking about it terrifies me.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} I'd like to learn about Arlan.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100021131-->
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 125.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Arlan went to dress his wounds at the rest area. He knows himself well... but if he insists on pushing his limits, I'll give him a good earful.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 126.ogg}} '''Asta:''' I'm very upset he didn't obey my orders and insisted on searching the storage zone even though everyone had already evacuated.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 127.ogg}} '''Asta:''' I know he didn't want to leave any researchers behind... The Security Department is more than just a job to him.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 128.ogg}} '''Asta:''' But Arlan doesn't care about getting hurt, he only cares about protecting others. It's the only way he feels... fulfilled.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 129.ogg}} '''Asta:''' And it's not that I don't understand where he's coming from. I just want him to look out for himself, too!
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} I'd like to learn about Herta.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100021137-->
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 130.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Herta... she's a member of the Genius Society. One of the proud favorites of the Aeon of Erudition. Ever since the birth of {{Rubi|Nous|Aeon of Erudition}}, there have only been 84 people admitted into the Genius Society.
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 131.ogg}} '''Asta:''' That is why Madam Herta is extremely... headstrong... She only pursues what interests her and as soon as that interest is lost, she abandons it and moves on. The space station was one such abandoned interest...
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 132.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Anyway, I lent out one of her manuscripts as a resource reference not long ago. It should still be in the master control zone. You can take a look if you wish.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't have any more questions.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_100021141-->
:::{{A|VO chapter0 3 asta 133.ogg}} '''Asta:''' Huh, chatting with you seems to have lightened my mood. It seems like talking can really raise one's spirits.
